para.verbatim:
///
/// Sketch of a stimset with three test pulse like epochs
///
///                    +-----+       +-----+       +-----+
///                    |     |       |     |       |     |
///                    |     |       |     |       |     |
///                    |     |       |     |       |     |
/// -------------------+     +-------+     +-------+     +------------------------
///
/// Epoch borders
/// -------------
///
///                |   |     |   |   |     |   |   |     |   |
///
/// So for this stimset we have two epochs at the very beginning and end, plus
/// three epochs per test pulse and three test pulses, which gives eleven in
/// total.
///
///
